<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"> 
</head>
<body>
    <%-include('partials/header')%> 
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Who I am</h2>
            <p>
                Hi, I’m Aakansha! Just your average girl who decided to dive into the wild world of web development. I’m here to build cool stuff, break things (and hopefully fix them), and maybe, just maybe, make the internet a slightly better place. If I can help solve a problem or two along the way, that’s a bonus!
            </section>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>My Mission</h2>
            <p>
                My mission is to create a space where book lovers can share their thoughts, discover new reads, and connect with others who share their passion. Whether you’re here to write reviews or find your next favorite book, I hope this platform makes the experience enjoyable and meaningful.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>What I Offer</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>A simple and user-friendly platform to share and explore book reviews.</li>
                <li>A growing community of readers and writers who love books as much as I do.</li>
                <li>A space to learn, grow, and connect over shared interests.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>My Story</h2>
            <p>
                It all started with a simple idea: to create a platform where people can share their love for books. As someone who’s always been fascinated by stories and technology, this project felt like the perfect way to combine both. Along the way, I’ve learned so much about web development, design, and the power of community.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Join Us</h2>
            <p>
                Ready to dive in? Explore the website, share your thoughts on your favorite books, or just say hi. I’d love to hear from you and grow this community together. Let’s make this space a little brighter, one book review at a time!
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Contact Me</a>
        </section>
    </div>
    <%-include('partials/footer')%>
</body>
</html>